main.bio: Hi there! I'm Ajay! A passionate & Experienced Full Stack Web Developer having an experience of building web applications with JavaScript/ Reactjs / Nodejs / HTML / CSS / NoSQL / Java / Python and some other cool libraries and frameworks. Hands-on experience in DevOps using Docker, Kubernetes, Azure DevOps, Terraform, Jenkins & Ansible across AWS, Azure & GCP. Proficient with Configuration Management tools, and in developing CI/CD pipelines & IaC. Strong engineering professional with a Bachelor of Engineering focused in Computer Science. An innovator, known for designing solutions to building and optimising the performance of user-centric high impact website. Leverage technical, analytical and problem-solving skills to create dynamic, high-speed websites, apps and platform fueling competitive advantage and revenue growth.apps and platform fueling competitive advantage and revenue growth.
